{"tid":425294,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]屋企揸住兩層私樓，有咩方法可以住公屋？","createTime":"2017-10-05T15:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T13:56:37.000Z","uid":87511,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2f716a84eb0ec9507b7195047f28cbe0ce71c3a6","tid":425294,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"兩層都冇我名<br />\n而且對上我仲有兩個哥哥<br />\n我屋企又係啲重男輕女嘅家庭<br />\n兩層樓就肯定冇我份架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過想去輪公屋,但係正苦啲人一知道我屋企揸住兩層私樓......<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我成功輪到公屋,厚酬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絕不食言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n利申: 絲,借朋友AC問"},{"pid":"f3a22b1e0dffe18e0492f9ba712efec3ac34bd51","tid":425294,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"你無收入就ok"},{"pid":"6490c0a707f5e5bb8691a4e184e4244c8480c511","tid":425294,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc7227248e9d5b09e83140bcf8eb5801c4244f7a","tid":425294,"uid":48579,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"唔洗啦 直接比人包咪得"},{"pid":"3bf63254aa97bce706c70a8a7c4172b452f0a515","tid":425294,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"205ad6eab015ea7d8ad02de735b4777998dfe6e5","tid":425294,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單人表咪得<br />\n屋企人有錢唔等於你有錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我睇房署個單人申請須知,係話正苦會睇埋屋企人資產總值&amp;有冇持有物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/common/pdf/global-elements/forms/flat-application/HD274.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcommon%2Fpdf%2Fglobal-elements%2Fforms%2Fflat-application%2FHD274.pdf&d=IbKkGM7vAtr1qWKz%2FZPBocn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1ad003f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/common/pdf/global-elements/forms/flat-application/HD274.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n第4頁<br />\n2.1.5 &amp; 2.1.6"},{"pid":"1564bc29b3cdc4c4226c8e3111c03d80370c2086","tid":425294,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>單人表咪得<br />\n屋企人有錢唔等於你有錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我睇房署個單人申請須知,係話正苦會睇埋屋企人資產總值&amp;有冇持有物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/common/pdf/global-elements/forms/flat-application/HD274.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcommon%2Fpdf%2Fglobal-elements%2Fforms%2Fflat-application%2FHD274.pdf&d=IbKkGM7vAtr1qWKz%2FZPBocn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1ad003f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/common/pdf/global-elements/forms/flat-application/HD274.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n第4頁<br />\n2.1.5 &amp; 2.1.6</blockquote><br />\n但係去到最底 2.1.10<br />\n又話「 如屬一人申請，以上各項只適用於申請人。」<br />\n<br />\n好鳩亂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e999336437107f800b55c6f86e9a23993667905","tid":425294,"uid":47005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"你扮有精神病，扮自殺俾人救番，搵個區議員，記得係淫賤聯ge<br />\n<br />\n咁就同你安排上樓架啦"},{"pid":"d968baedd5eb450da99805c3fdf89ff6ddb682b8","tid":425294,"uid":26419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>單人表咪得<br />\n屋企人有錢唔等於你有錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我睇房署個單人申請須知,係話正苦會睇埋屋企人資產總值&amp;有冇持有物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/common/pdf/global-elements/forms/flat-application/HD274.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcommon%2Fpdf%2Fglobal-elements%2Fforms%2Fflat-application%2FHD274.pdf&d=IbKkGM7vAtr1qWKz%2FZPBocn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1ad003f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/common/pdf/global-elements/forms/flat-application/HD274.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n第4頁<br />\n2.1.5 &amp; 2.1.6</blockquote><br />\n但係去到最底 2.1.10<br />\n又話「 如屬一人申請，以上各項只適用於申請人。」<br />\n<br />\n好鳩亂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企有幾層 無一間冩我名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣可以申請到"},{"pid":"eef5af13d20bfacdbee9a744d93e9e38877d7b5a","tid":425294,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8b6df44981a101334d2436b76ba53c0ad7337b4","tid":425294,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"279cc3cb85b86a286e7979365d57b9c87f3b6c9d","tid":425294,"uid":124791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"搵個單身廢老嫁俾佢&gt;佢間公屋加你個名&gt;踢廢老入老人院<br />\n<br />\n得咗"},{"pid":"ace239be9df99a31bb3d0de3f974bab2703d3b7d","tid":425294,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"叫你屋企人買多間囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ae3e787622665832a0030b92089632dce12bc0","tid":425294,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T18:46:03.000Z","msg":"同男朋友結婚<br />\n結完就生小朋友<br />\n小朋友出世就即離婚<br />\n到時話男人唔要小朋友同自己"},{"pid":"ccfaa0cef75dfad36a058132605dfe6589a41981","tid":425294,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩層都冇我名<br />\n而且對上我仲有兩個哥哥<br />\n我屋企又係啲重男輕女嘅家庭<br />\n兩層樓就肯定冇我份架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過想去輪公屋,但係正苦啲人一知道我屋企揸住兩層私樓......<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我成功輪到公屋,厚酬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絕不食言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n利申: 絲,借朋友AC問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n妳淨係報自己低能就得架啦<br />\n<br />\nbtw 假設妳認真又夠18歲<br />\n佢拎張表申請就得<br />\n妳老豆係李嘉誠都申請得，<br />\n18歲就係獨立個體"},{"pid":"6d873d96e1f8353ae5643430cab9e51e0f25e340","tid":425294,"uid":103317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:54:00.000Z","msg":"轉兩層樓落我名<br />\n成家一齊輪都得"},{"pid":"d165ed31d49e08af7671a13704e604ea8b191130","tid":425294,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/035942_6c17cf47c93f52d63dc833e6c263570a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F035942_6c17cf47c93f52d63dc833e6c263570a.jpg&h=725af832&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18a32a253ab43b89d014d0642b65a6eac0d40b75","tid":425294,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T20:17:53.000Z","msg":"1. 自己一個排 ＞ 申請唔可以過限額 ＞ 計分制下至少要五十歲 ＞ 每四五年可能寄信抽查 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n2. 同其中一個哥哥（冇樓）排 ＞ 申請同審查唔可以過限額＞六七年之後審查 / 七八年上樓 ＞期間如果有人結婚要踢另一個 ＞ 上樓阿哥同你爭 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n3. 結婚之後排（老公冇樓）＞同哥哥輪差唔到 ＞ 睇樓主有排都唔會結婚 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n4. 搵個冇樓嘅阿爺阿婆一齊排 ＞申請同審查唔可以過限額＞四五年上樓 ＞ 前題老人家要建在  <br />\n<br />\n5. 叫阿爺阿婆自己排（一或二人) ＞ 四五年＞ 排到加你名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家真係好多人利用老人家上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27af8216d02ca7e97728adae38572f2413d6529","tid":425294,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T20:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 自己一個排 ＞ 申請唔可以過限額 ＞ 計分制下至少要五十歲 ＞ 每四五年可能寄信抽查 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n2. 同其中一個哥哥（冇樓）排 ＞ 申請同審查唔可以過限額＞六七年之後審查 / 七八年上樓 ＞期間如果有人結婚要踢另一個 ＞ 上樓阿哥同你爭 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n3. 結婚之後排（老公冇樓）＞同哥哥輪差唔到 ＞ 睇樓主有排都唔會結婚 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n4. 搵個冇樓嘅阿爺阿婆一齊排 ＞申請同審查唔可以過限額＞四五年上樓 ＞ 前題老人家要建在  <br />\n<br />\n5. 叫阿爺阿婆自己排（一或二人) ＞ 四五年＞ 排到加你名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家真係好多人利用老人家上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二宗案件為該家庭子女的涉案，兒子林偉聰(三十二歲)及林佩賢(二十九歲)同被控一項欺詐罪名，違反《盜竊罪條例》第16A條，兄妹二人涉嫌虛報與外祖母同住，利用「家有長者優先配屋計劃」要求「極速配屋」，但其後被揭發外祖母在明愛馮黃鳳亭安老院居住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過如果我識你 我會舉報你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0857eeabb4030d48e9b466d31c57540055aacab6","tid":425294,"uid":5971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"簽衰仔紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f58893d00763102cba33ccdac33bdc0352a5d50","tid":425294,"uid":19484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:25:25.000Z","msg":"屋企有樓就唔好同人爭公屋啦<br />\n我諗佢地應該都會比你有一個住既地方 唔洗太擔心"},{"pid":"bc84b4a4ddf5b55532d02ca4c9c16de2fb6daa64","tid":425294,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:46:31.000Z","msg":"申請單人公屋 唔洗查你屋企人<br />\n不過排到2046"},{"pid":"5e7f4296d62fdb29fec0f3c9d86cf696aaee1720","tid":425294,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:14:57.000Z","msg":"一個申請，入息唔過要求就得"},{"pid":"55525d853cabc41876a926a4888728f4ae9e5026","tid":425294,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 自己一個排 ＞ 申請唔可以過限額 ＞ 計分制下至少要五十歲 ＞ 每四五年可能寄信抽查 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n2. 同其中一個哥哥（冇樓）排 ＞ 申請同審查唔可以過限額＞六七年之後審查 / 七八年上樓 ＞期間如果有人結婚要踢另一個 ＞ 上樓阿哥同你爭 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n3. 結婚之後排（老公冇樓）＞同哥哥輪差唔到 ＞ 睇樓主有排都唔會結婚 ＞ 收皮<br />\n<br />\n4. 搵個冇樓嘅阿爺阿婆一齊排 ＞申請同審查唔可以過限額＞四五年上樓 ＞ 前題老人家要建在  <br />\n<br />\n5. 叫阿爺阿婆自己排（一或二人) ＞ 四五年＞ 排到加你名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家真係好多人利用老人家上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第五嗰個方法唔得， 排到後加名都只係暫住，兩老死後，你都要搬走。"},{"pid":"5b5b67053a5e28fe95aedec1e001373ba5f6dcf1","tid":425294,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}